.2, all probed by the AKARI satellite. The next generation space infrared\ntelescope, SPICA, will revolutionize our view of the infrared Universe with\nsuperb sensitivity of the cooled 3m space telescope. We conclude with our\nsurvey proposal and future prospects with SPICA.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Jun 2015 20:00:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-07-01"}
