ories, such as the ones we\nintroduce here, are necessary to study diffusion on long timescales.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 29 Jun 2015 21:18:31 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 11 Aug 2015 15:27:03 GMT"}],"update_date":"2015-10-28"}
